#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.cat"
msgstr "# triton.language.cat"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.cat`函数用于将指定的tensor进行拼接。"
msgstr "Introduction: The `triton.language.cat` function is used to concatenate specified tensors."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.cat(input, other, can_reorder=False, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                  | 说明                                   |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------------- |\n"
"| `input`           | `Tensor`               | 拼接的第一个tensor |\n"
"| `other`            | `Tensor`               | 拼接的第二个tensor |\n"
"| `can_reorder`            | `Bool`               | 重新排序 – 编译器提示。如果为真，编译器在连接输入时允许重新排序元素。仅支持can_reorder=True。  |\n"
"| `_semantic`            | `Optional[str]`               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ---- | ----------- |\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | The first tensor to concatenate |\n"
"| `other` | `Tensor` | The second tensor to concatenate |\n"
"| `can_reorder` | `Bool` | Reorder – compiler hint. If true, the compiler allows reordering elements when concatenating inputs. Only `can_reorder=True` is supported. |\n"
"| `_semantic` | `Optional[str]` | Reserved parameter; external calls are not currently supported |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：完成拼接之后的tensor\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: The tensor after concatenation.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:20
msgid ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | × | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU支持 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | × | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU Support | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:22
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:24
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异。cat 只支持1D shape 的拼接。"
msgstr "Conclusion: There is no difference between GPU and Ascend platform in terms of Shape. cat only supports concatenation of 1D shapes."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:26
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:28
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:30
msgid ""
"1.ASCEND和CUDA都只支持 can_reorder=True，即拼接tensor后重新排序。\n"
"2.cat 只支持1D shape 的拼接。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. Both ASCEND and CUDA only support `can_reorder=True`, meaning the tensors are reordered after concatenation.  \n"
"2. `cat` only supports concatenation for 1D shapes.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:32
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:34
msgid "以下示例实现了对1D shape的两个tensor进行的拼接："
msgstr "The following example demonstrates the concatenation of two tensors with a 1D shape:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/cat.md:36
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"import torch\n"
"import torch_npu\n"
"import pytest\n"
"import test_common\n"
"import math\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def fn_npu_(output_ptr, x_ptr, y_ptr, XB: tl.constexpr):\n"
"\n"
"    idx = tl.arange(0, XB)\n"
"    X = tl.load(x_ptr + idx)\n"
"    Y = tl.load(y_ptr + idx)\n"
"\n"
"    ret = tl.cat(X, Y, can_reorder=True)\n"
"\n"
"    oidx = tl.arange(0, XB * 2)\n"
"\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + oidx, ret)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## The CAT operator in the Triton community also does not support boolean types.\n"
"@pytest.mark.parametrize('shape', [(32,), (741,)]) #triton only support 1D cat\n"
"@pytest.mark.parametrize('dtype', ['float32',])\n"
"def test_cat(shape, dtype):\n"
"    m = shape[0]\n"
"    x = torch.full((m, ), 100, dtype=eval(\"torch.\" + dtype)).npu()\n"
"    y = torch.full((m, ), 30, dtype=eval(\"torch.\" + dtype)).npu()\n"
"\n"
"    output = torch.randint(1, (m * 2, ), dtype=eval(\"torch.\" + dtype)).npu()\n"
"\n"
"    ans = torch.cat((x, y), dim=0)\n"
"\n"
"    fn_npu_[1, 1, 1](output, x, y, m)\n"
"\n"
"    test_common.validate_cmp(dtype, ans, output)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

